            Jamie Flynn
          
          
            
              I am currently senior at Oregon State University studying Natural Resources with a specialization in Natural Resource Education. I am currently working at Oregon State University as START Leader. I am a classically trained data scientist living in the San Francisco Bay Area. Currently I work on the Oculus team at Facebook. I love talking about baseball, true crime podcasts, and causal inference.
